<br>
BTW, please don't think that Eden is supposed to be Earth 'cause it isn't. this story has nothing to do with &quot;our&quot; universe or reality. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
